#

Chipotle Lime Chicken with Cilantro Rice

$15.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Tags:

MexicanGrilledSavoryHealthy

Description

Zesty chipotle chicken served on a bed of fragrant cilantro lime rice, topped with fresh avocado and pico de gallo for a burst of flavor!

Ingredients

  • Chicken Breasts: 4 pieces
  • Chipotle in Adobo Sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • Lime Juice: 1/4 cup
  • Cilantro: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • Rice: 1 cup
  • Chicken Broth: 2 cups
  • Avocado: 1, sliced
  • Pico de Gallo: 1 cup
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
